<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
 <head> 
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
 </head>
 <body>	
    <h1>THE CHEESE BLOCKS TALE</h1>
<p>    There once was a block of cheese. Their name was ___(mc). ___ (mc) was the COOLEST/AWESOMEST/GNARLIEST cheese block in town, 
    and they strutted through the streets with cheesy pride. ___ (best friend) was ___ ‘s (mc) best friend. They were always attached at their halloumi hips. 
    They never went anywhere without one another until… </p>
    <p>	___(mc) GOT A GIRLFRIEND!!!  Her name was ___ (gf)! Suddenly ___(mc) got dragged away from ___(bsf) all the time! 
        No longer always together, ___(bsf) felt all alone. Soon, he realized he needed to go get some sort of revenge on ___(gf). 
        HE WANTED HIS BEST FRIEND BACK!!! </p>
        <p>	On the other side of Cheddartopia, ___(mc) was starting to feel entrapped by their girlfriend. 
            She never let them see anyone else, only her, using up their entire free time. 
            It made ___(mc) very sad. They missed ___(bsf) very much. They began to realize that ___(gf) wasn’t a good person! 
            They began to wish they could escape from their relationship.
            <p>	Back at ___’s (bsf) house, ___(bsf) was brainstorming like crazy. He could turn ___(gf) into fondue/grilled cheese/cream cheese! 
                There were so many evil options. Finally, with an idea in mind, ___’s(bsf) scheming could begin. 
                 A part of his mozzarella mind felt bad, but then he realized that ___(mc) needs saving from ___(gf).</p>

</p>
<h1>	WHAT IS ___’S(bsf) PLAN?!</h1>
<h1>Piano attack!?</h1>
<h1>A superhero cape!?</h1>
<h1>Have a talk!?</h1>
<h1>Run into a rock!?</h1>
<h1>Add immense details!?</h1>
    <p>	Back where ___(mc) was, ___(gf) had locked them in a cage! 
        She was actually a super villain who liked kidnapping poor cheesy souls and turning them into swiss cheese. 
        She had a malicious laugh/face/identity. They wished that ___(bsf) was there, but sadly, he wasn’t. 
        They tried escaping, but ___(gf) shot her cheese string at them, scaring them to the back of the cage.</p>
        <p>	ENDING ONE-
	Suddenly, through the roof of ___’s(gf) house, a piano came sailing down. 
    With a loud crash, it flattened ___(gf) instantly until she was all but seriously squished. 
    From the gaping hole above, ___(bsf) waved at ___(mc) saving the day.</p>
    <p>	ENDING TWO-
	Out of nowhere, a high pitch shriek came from outside the window. 
    Approaching the glass, ___(gf) fell over in terror as ___(bsf) smashed through with a red/green/purple cape. 
    He stopped heroically in front of ___’s(mc) cage, breaking it open and carrying them out of there. 
    The day was saved with the power of friendship.</p>
    <p>	ENDING THREE-
	A loud knocking sounded at the front door of the house. 
    Opening it, ___(gf) came face to face with ___(bsf). 
    He has big puppy dog eyes and a pouting lip, asking for ___(mc) back.
     ___(gf) looked him up and down VERY slowly. Then she cackled, slamming the door in ___’s(bsf) face.
      ___(mc) was trapped forever. Too bad, so sad.</p>
      <p>	ENDING FOUR-
	While heading to ___’s(gf) house, with his evil plan, ___(bsf) ran straight into a large… stone? 
    OH NO! IT’S A HUMAN! He tried to run, but suddenly a hand scooped him up. 
    Screaming like a mad munster cheese, he tried a feeble escape. Sadly, it was useless.
     ___(bsf) was no more in history than a cheesy snack for a human being. And ___(mc) was still trapped.</p>
     <p>ENDING FIVE-
	VERY long story short: ___’s(bsf) took centuries. 
    By the time it was ready to put in action, the world was dominated by the people of MURICA, evil colonizing beings who destroyed cheese.
     Cheesetopia was no more, and he wasn’t even sure if ___(mc) was still alive. Finally, with a plan prepared, ___(bsf) realized he couldn’t even put it in action!
      He was simply too old. A sad ending to a sad story. ___(bsf) never got to see his best friend ever again.</p>
</body>
